==English==
{{wikisource1911Enc|Abandonment}}
===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|abandonnement|lang=fr}}, from {{term|abandonner||to abandon, relinquish|lang=fr}}. {{term|abandonner|lang=fr}} was originally equivalent to {{term||mettre à bandon|to leave to the jurisdiction, i.e. of another|lang=fr}}, {{term|bandon|lang=fr}} being from {{etyl|ML.|en}} {{term|bandum|lang=la}}, {{term|bannum||order, decree, ban|lang=la}} (See also English {{term|banns|lang=en}}.)

